review: I find it funny that people have posted this place/location as closed... Um its not.  I've been there as recently as TONIGHT... still going strong.  I've only had an "issue" one time in the many times I've been there & that was a server who sorta ignored our table - as in, our drinks were gone and we were still there wanting more. So yeah.  Other than that the food is standard TGIF, staff is friendly & funny.   my only real complaint is that there are only two locations in "sacramento" (ELk Grove & Roseville) - I live in Carmichael, and was sad to see the Howe ave location shut down years ago.
